== 背景 ==
2018年5月，[[尼泊尔共产党（联合马列）|尼共(联合马列)]]与[[尼泊尔共产党（毛主义中心）|尼共(毛中心)]]合并为[[尼泊尔共产党_(2018年)|尼泊尔共产党]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=尼泊尔的两个主要政党合并组成尼泊尔共产党 - Xinhua {{!}} English.news.cn|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2018-05/18/c_137187121.htm|access-date=2020-12-30|website=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109034125/http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2018-05/18/c_137187121.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=两大共产党合并获得政府批准，新政党正式成立|url=http://myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com/news/41883/|access-date=2020-12-30|website=我的共和国|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923070530/https://myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com/news/41883/|dead-url=no}}</ref>两党领导人达成一份政治协议，同意对方将分担一半的总理任期。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Subedi |first1=Binu |title=नेकपा विवाद : घुमीफिरी मंसिर ४ |url=https://ekantipur.com/news/2020/08/24/159823166942739789.html |website=Ekantipur |publisher=Kailash Sirohiya |access-date=2020年12月31日 |archive-date=2020年10月17日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017070424/https://ekantipur.com/news/2020/08/24/159823166942739789.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年11月14日，在执政党党内一次高级会议上，执政党的内部矛盾爆发。<ref>{{Cite web|title=在高级会议上，达哈尔要求奥利牺牲自己以挽救党和共和国|url=https://kathmandupost.com/politics/2020/11/14/at-secretariat-meet-dahal-asks-oli-to-sacrifice-for-saving-party-and-republic|access-date=2020-12-30|website=kathmandupost.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128010802/https://kathmandupost.com/politics/2020/11/14/at-secretariat-meet-dahal-asks-oli-to-sacrifice-for-saving-party-and-republic|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=奥利在回应达哈尔的指控进行反击措施|url=https://kathmandupost.com/politics/2020/11/29/oli-goes-on-the-offensive-as-he-responds-to-dahal-s-allegations|access-date=2020-12-30|website=kathmandupost.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212152511/https://kathmandupost.com/politics/2020/11/29/oli-goes-on-the-offensive-as-he-responds-to-dahal-s-allegations|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=国会秘书处表示，众议院解散决定后，启动对奥利的不信任议案|url=https://kathmandupost.com/national/2020/12/23/parliament-secretariat-says-no-confidence-motion-against-oli-was-registered-after-house-dissolution-decision|access-date=2020-12-30|website=kathmandupost.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125175355/https://kathmandupost.com/national/2020/12/23/parliament-secretariat-says-no-confidence-motion-against-oli-was-registered-after-house-dissolution-decision|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Setopati|first=Setopati|title=准备进行对我的不信任动议：奥利议员|url=https://en.setopati.com/political/154669/|access-date=2020-12-30|website=Setopati|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108031655/https://en.setopati.com/political/154669/|dead-url=no}}</ref>为了抗议总理奥利的决定，七位政府部长宣布辞职。<ref>{{Cite web|title=来自共产党内的七位部长辞职|url=https://kathmandupost.com/politics/2020/12/20/seven-ministers-all-from-the-dahal-nepal-faction-in-ruling-party-resign-1608463576|access-date=2020-12-30|website=kathmandupost.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126144909/https://kathmandupost.com/politics/2020/12/20/seven-ministers-all-from-the-dahal-nepal-faction-in-ruling-party-resign-1608463576|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=7名尼泊尔部长因议会解散而辞职 - Xinhua {{!}} English.news.cn|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-12/20/c_139604926.htm|access-date=2020-12-30|website=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118011744/http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-12/20/c_139604926.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==选举制度==
275名尼泊尔众议院议员将通过两种方式选出：其中165名议员将通过单一选区[[領先者當選|簡單多數制]]而余下110名议员将通过[[封閉式名單|封閉式名單]]以[[比例代表制|比例代表制]]选出。<ref>[http://www.wipo.int/edocs/lexdocs/laws/en/np/np029en.pdf Article 84] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wipo.int/edocs/lexdocs/laws/en/np/np029en.pdf |date=20171117200359 }} Constitution of Nepal</ref>通过[[比例代表制|比例代表制]]方式选出的政党或是联盟有3%的选举门槛。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kafle|first1=Narayn|title=स‌ंसद्  र प्रदेशको निर्वाचन विधेयक पारित|url=http://gorkhapatraonline.com/epaper/showimage?img=uploads/epaper/2017-09-05/d5dc862970aa8746d2409f4855e61ae7.jpg|accessdate=6 September 2017|work=Gorkhapatra|publisher=Gorkhapatra Sansthan|date=5 September 2017|archive-date=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906223902/http://gorkhapatraonline.com/epaper/showimage?img=uploads%2Fepaper%2F2017-09-05%2Fd5dc862970aa8746d2409f4855e61ae7.jpg|dead-url=no}}</ref>

